我們讓你去接電話

148
00:09:41,338 --> 00:09:42,498
But do you have the guts to do it?
可是…

149
00:09:44,241 --> 00:09:45,868
你敢接嗎？

150
00:09:49,713 --> 00:09:51,681
Have I been bad to you?
我對你們不好嗎？

151
00:09:52,516 --> 00:09:54,381
Have I been bad to you?
我對你們不好嗎？

152
00:09:55,586 --> 00:09:56,348
Kojima..
小島…

153
00:09:58,122 --> 00:10:01,091
Is this how you repay me?
這就是你們報答我的動作嗎？

154
00:10:01,191 --> 00:10:04,388
I can't fight back if you want me dead
你們要殺我，我無法抵抗

155
00:10:05,696 --> 00:10:06,993
But the Japanese government
will do anything to punish you
但是我們日本政府

156
00:10:07,097 --> 00:10:09,895
一定會因此對你們展開討伐…

157
00:10:12,703 --> 00:10:15,103
We might as well die together
大家同歸於盡吧！

158
00:10:17,074 --> 00:10:18,063
Kojima!
小島…

159
00:10:22,980 --> 00:10:26,848
We have airplanes, but do you?
我們有飛機，你們有嗎？

160
00:10:27,351 --> 00:10:31,447
We have machineguns and cannons,
but do you?
我們有機槍大砲，你們有嗎？

161
00:10:32,923 --> 00:10:37,417
Think about
how Mouna Rudo used to insult you
想想莫那魯道是怎麼羞辱你們的…

162
00:10:37,961 --> 00:10:41,795
Last time when we're out hunting
they threatened to kill you all
上次打獵他們還揚言要殺光你們

163
00:10:41,899 --> 00:10:43,958
Don't you remember?
你們難道忘記了嗎？

164
00:10:45,369 --> 00:10:47,599
Are you willing to die
with them in the battlefield?
現在還要陪他們一起戰死嗎？

165
00:10:48,972 --> 00:10:50,837
Temu Walis,
鐵木瓦力斯？

166
00:10:50,941 --> 00:10:53,273
you won't have the chance to grow up
…我不會讓你長大的！

167
00:11:02,186 --> 00:11:03,016
Hello?
喂…

168
00:11:06,523 --> 00:11:07,490
Hello?
喂…

169
00:11:07,591 --> 00:11:10,822
Take it easy! There's more!
不要搶，還有…別急…

170
00:11:11,628 --> 00:11:13,619
Hurry up!
動作快一點！

171
00:11:13,731 --> 00:11:14,993
Come on!
快一點！

172
00:11:18,035 --> 00:11:19,502
Come on!
快一點！

173
00:11:23,741 --> 00:11:25,538
Chief Mouna?
莫那頭目…

174
00:11:40,357 --> 00:11:41,483
Thank you
謝謝你…

175
00:11:44,762 --> 00:11:45,626
Thank you
謝謝你！

176
00:11:46,296 --> 00:11:47,126
Thank you
謝謝你！

177
00:11:48,132 --> 00:11:50,225
Thank you
謝謝你們！

178
00:11:50,334 --> 00:11:53,201
Thank you. Thank you all
謝謝…真的謝謝你們！

179
00:11:54,238 --> 00:11:55,136
Thank you
謝謝你們！

180
00:11:55,239 --> 00:11:56,331
Thank you -Come on!
-謝謝你們！
-快一點…

181
00:11:57,541 --> 00:11:59,065
Thank you. Thank you all
謝謝！謝謝你們！

182
00:12:01,945 --> 00:12:02,468
Thank you
謝謝你們！

183
00:12:02,579 --> 00:12:03,443
Tado!
達多！

184
00:12:03,547 --> 00:12:05,242
Sapu, where's my father?
薩布，我父親呢？

185
00:12:06,850 --> 00:12:10,217
What's going on? Why did they want us back?
到底在搞什麼？叫我們回來？

186
00:12:18,228 --> 00:12:18,990
Father, why did you give up Hakaw Supeitei?
父親…

187
00:12:19,096 --> 00:12:21,155
為什麼要放棄人止關呢？

188
00:12:21,265 --> 00:12:22,857
So you're back!
回來了啊？

189
00:12:28,105 --> 00:12:30,403
Come on, let's go back to our clan
走！回部落去…

190
00:12:30,507 --> 00:12:31,804
Back to our clan? You're giving up here as well?
回部落？

191
00:12:31,909 --> 00:12:33,809
…連這裡也不要了？

192
00:12:33,911 --> 00:12:35,037
Tado, you can't think like the Japanese
when fighting them
達多…

193
00:12:35,279 --> 00:12:38,806
和日本人打仗不能用日本人的想法…

194
00:12:38,916 --> 00:12:41,316
You have to think like the wind
要用風的想法…

195
00:12:41,418 --> 00:12:42,885
The wind?
風？

196
00:12:44,254 --> 00:12:46,245
The wind is invisible
風是看不見的…

197
00:12:54,898 --> 00:12:56,024
Baso, give up everything, everyone
and come back to the clan with me
巴索…

198
00:12:56,133 --> 00:12:59,034
東西都別拿了，所有人回部落！

199
00:13:00,537 --> 00:13:01,299
Japanese airplanes!
日本飛機…

200
00:13:01,405 --> 00:13:03,100
Over there! -Fire!
-在那邊…
-開槍！

201
00:13:05,876 --> 00:13:07,935
Shoot it! Come on!
開槍打他！快點！

202
00:13:11,582 --> 00:13:12,549
Are you so scared?
這麼害怕嗎？

203
00:13:16,620 --> 00:13:19,111
Are you really so scared?
真的這麼害怕嗎？

204
00:13:29,233 --> 00:13:33,932
I went head hunting for the first time
when I was 15
十五歲那年，我第一次出草…

205
00:13:35,873 --> 00:13:39,570
I was so nervous
that my arms and legs were trembling
我也緊張膽怯，我的手腳發抖…

206
00:13:40,878 --> 00:13:45,281
But my eyes were sharp as arrows
但是…我的眼神如箭！

207
00:13:46,416 --> 00:13:48,577
As soon as I cut the enemy's head off
揮下敵人首級的瞬間…

208
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:52,684
I forgot what it was like to be scared
我忘記了什麼叫害怕！

209
00:13:54,191 --> 00:13:55,954
because I knew I'd go back to my clan
因為我知道…

210
00:13:57,194 --> 00:14:01,187
to feast and celebrate, being treated as a hero
我將英雄地回到部落接受酒宴歡慶

211
00:14:03,367 --> 00:14:05,699
because I knew that all my people
因為我知道…

212
00:14:05,802 --> 00:14:10,705
male and female, young and old
從今以後部落裡的男女老少…

213
00:14:10,807 --> 00:14:13,537
would respect me for my bravery
都將尊敬我的勇敢！

214
00:14:13,644 --> 00:14:15,544
However, it's different this time
可是…

215
00:14:15,646 --> 00:14:17,773
這次不一樣

216
00:14:23,186 --> 00:14:25,984
We successfully offered a blood sacrifice
to our ancestors today
今天我們雖然成功地血祭了祖靈

217
00:14:28,225 --> 00:14:31,353
and are now qualified
to stride over the rainbow bridge
取得了通過彩虹橋的資格

218
00:14:31,461 --> 00:14:34,225
but what awaits us now is not a festive feast
不過接下來所要面對的…

219
00:14:34,331 --> 00:14:36,424
不是歡慶的酒宴

220
00:14:36,533 --> 00:14:39,297
but to choose how we die
而是選擇死亡的方式！

221
00:14:39,403 --> 00:14:41,200
Run the electricity!
送電！

222
00:14:44,408 --> 00:14:46,774
Before we initiated the revolt
早在起事之前…

223
00:14:46,877 --> 00:14:51,041
you knew it'd turn out like this, didn't you?
你們就知道這種結果了，不是嗎？

224
00:14:51,248 --> 00:14:53,011
My children..
孩子們…

225
00:14:54,718 --> 00:14:56,686
...don't be scared
別急著害怕！

226
00:14:57,955 --> 00:15:01,652
You've been very brave today
你們今天表現得很勇敢

227
00:15:02,526 --> 00:15:05,017
Our ancestors' spirits have seen it all
祖靈們一定也看見了

228
00:15:05,128 --> 00:15:08,461
But the battle to come is the real one
但接下來要面對的才是真正的戰鬥

229
00:15:08,565 --> 00:15:12,524
It's a battle that will terrify the invaders
是要讓異族人嚇破膽的戰鬥…

230
00:15:12,903 --> 00:15:14,131
Someone's here!
有人來了…

231
00:15:14,237 --> 00:15:18,799
Sisin babblers in the forests
are driving off the scavenging crows
森林的祖靈鳥正驅趕著吃腐肉的烏鴉

232
00:15:18,909 --> 00:15:24,040
The rainbow will be more beautiful
in the sunlight after the rain
水氣後的陽光只會讓彩虹更艷麗…

233
00:15:26,049 --> 00:15:28,643
It's a bunch of Hans from Wushe
是從霧社下來的漢人

234
00:15:30,787 --> 00:15:32,778
Lock them all up!
把他們通通關起來…

235
00:15:41,565 --> 00:15:44,295
My children..
孩子啊…

236
00:15:44,401 --> 00:15:46,392
...don't be afraid
別害怕！

237
00:15:47,904 --> 00:15:53,274
Our ancestors' spirits know we're good warriors
guarding our hunting grounds
祖靈會肯定我們是守護獵場的好戰士

238
00:15:54,711 --> 00:15:57,805
The blood stains on your hands can prove it
你們手上的血痕就是印記

239
00:15:57,914 --> 00:16:00,940
Every one of you is a Seediq Bale
你們已經是個賽德克巴萊

240
00:16:02,219 --> 00:16:04,949
Remember, you have to be proud
記住…

241
00:16:05,055 --> 00:16:07,990
要驕傲！

242
00:16:08,091 --> 00:16:11,288
Let's cross the rainbow bridge together
彩虹橋上我們一起過！

243
00:16:58,108 --> 00:17:00,338
Nobody's guarding here
沒人防守啊…

244
00:17:00,444 --> 00:17:03,345
Not a single soul on this path
整條路上上下下全是空的！

245
00:17:06,383 --> 00:17:08,146
How could it be?
怎麼可能？

246
00:17:14,357 --> 00:17:15,847
Advance!
前進…

247
00:17:15,959 --> 00:17:17,017
Wait!
等一下！

248
00:17:17,127 --> 00:17:19,357
Stop! Halt!
停！停下來！

249
00:17:20,130 --> 00:17:21,722
Don't rush uphill
I know these savages all too well
先別上去…

250
00:17:21,832 --> 00:17:24,528
我太了解這些生蕃了…

251
00:17:35,145 --> 00:17:37,170
What a chilly night!
怎麼這麼冷啊…

252
00:17:39,649 --> 00:17:41,981
It's warm here
這個好暖和…

253
00:18:04,307 --> 00:18:06,138
Savages!
有生蕃！

254
00:18:13,416 --> 00:18:14,883
Hold the fire!
停火！

255
00:18:17,320 --> 00:18:26,058
l'm trekking over the high mountains
我走在高山峻嶺上

256
00:18:26,163 --> 00:18:35,333
The creek water is so thick and muddy
溪水是那麼地混濁

257
00:18:35,438 --> 00:18:44,710
l can't help but shed my tears
我忍不住掉下眼淚

258
00:18:44,815 --> 00:18:54,122
l'm walking along a wide road
我沿著寬敞的大路走

259
00:19:00,564 --> 00:19:02,156
He's asleep
他睡著了…

260
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:12,105
Ichiro?
一郎…

261
00:19:12,209 --> 00:19:16,043
Today is our wedding anniversary
今天是我們的結婚紀念日

262
00:19:16,146 --> 00:19:18,239
You remember, don't you?
…你記得嗎？

263
00:19:23,186 --> 00:19:32,458
We're walking on
with perseverance and determination
我們要坦蕩堅忍地走下去…

264
00:19:32,562 --> 00:19:41,436
We can't fall asleep anymore
已經無法入睡了…

265
00:19:41,538 --> 00:19:50,640
Let's go back to the heavenly home
of our ancestors
快點回祖靈之家呀…

266
00:19:52,849 --> 00:19:53,645
Kojima!
小島！

267
00:19:54,284 --> 00:19:55,717
Long time no see
好久不見了…

268
00:19:56,152 --> 00:19:57,050
Captain!
隊長！

269
00:19:58,521 --> 00:19:59,920
Let me introduce you, Captain
我來向你介紹

270
00:20:00,557 --> 00:20:03,253
This is the chief of Tnbarah Clan, Temu Walis
這位是屯巴拉社頭目鐵木瓦力斯…

271
00:20:05,729 --> 00:20:07,287
Got a good head on his shoulders
聰明的傢伙！

272
00:20:09,499 --> 00:20:10,466
Kojima?
小島…

273
00:20:15,338 --> 00:20:19,274
I heard all your family were killed in the venue?
聽說你的家人都在會場上被殺了？

274
00:20:19,376 --> 00:20:21,344
We will seek revenge
…我們會報復的！

275
00:20:54,244 --> 00:20:56,371
Attack!
突擊！

276
00:21:16,866 --> 00:21:19,562
Officer, nothing here
警部，什麼都沒有啊…

277
00:21:22,205 --> 00:21:23,638
Officer Goto!
後藤警部！

278
00:21:33,883 --> 00:21:37,375
What the hell are these savages up to?
…這些蕃人到底想幹嘛？

279
00:21:48,631 --> 00:21:51,429
The Japanese are coming!
日本人來了…

280
00:22:31,941 --> 00:22:33,932
Look behind you -Yeah
-小心後面…-是！

281
00:22:35,812 --> 00:22:38,542
This clan is over here
這個部落是那邊…

282
00:22:38,648 --> 00:22:41,481
This clan is over there
然後這個部落在那邊…

283
00:22:41,584 --> 00:22:44,576
Behind them is a creek
後面有一條溪流…

284
00:22:47,090 --> 00:22:48,421
Where do the Hans live? -The Hans..
那平常漢人都住在哪裡？

285
00:22:48,525 --> 00:22:50,584
漢人是…

286
00:22:52,295 --> 00:22:54,320
We're under attack! Duck!
有攻擊…趴下！

287
00:22:54,431 --> 00:22:55,796
Hide!
快躲起來！

288
00:23:11,247 --> 00:23:13,147
Awata! Awata!
粟田…粟田…

289
00:23:13,249 --> 00:23:14,807
Contact the Oizumi Squad
and find out where they are now
問一下大泉中隊

290
00:23:14,918 --> 00:23:17,011
看他們到哪裡了…

291
00:23:29,632 --> 00:23:32,294
This is Wushe Substation
這是霧社分室！這是霧社分室！

292
00:23:32,402 --> 00:23:34,927
This is Oizumi Squad
這是大泉中隊！這是大泉中隊！

293
00:23:35,505 --> 00:23:37,473
We're now by Suku Creek
我們現在在斯庫溪…斯庫溪…

294
00:23:37,574 --> 00:23:40,372
We're ambushed by the savages.
We need back up
正遭到蕃人的伏擊…請求支援…

295
00:23:40,477 --> 00:23:42,240
We're stuck in the creek water
現在被困在水中…

296
00:23:47,383 --> 00:23:51,217
Oizumi Squad..
大泉中隊！大泉中隊…

297
00:23:53,356 --> 00:23:54,118
Captain?
大尉…

298
00:23:54,224 --> 00:23:57,785
Assemble a banzai squad for a suicide charge
組織敢死隊，衝上去…

299
00:24:01,598 --> 00:24:03,429
Where is Yamada Police Squad?
山田警察隊呢？

300
00:24:39,702 --> 00:24:40,828
Charge!
衝啊！

301
00:24:44,807 --> 00:24:45,899
Pihu, let's go!
比荷！走了！

302
00:24:58,621 --> 00:25:00,350
Watch out! Dodge!
危險！閃開！

303
00:25:00,456 --> 00:25:02,947
Duck! Seek cover!
閃開！閃開！

304
00:25:21,778 --> 00:25:24,576
The women and children
from Boarung Clan are all here
波阿崙的婦孺都來了…

305
00:25:25,748 --> 00:25:27,010
Come on, let's go!
我們快點了！

306
00:25:33,356 --> 00:25:36,553
Have you packed up enough clothes, Mahung?
馬紅，衣服有多帶嗎？

307
00:25:36,659 --> 00:25:38,024
Yes, I have
有…

308
00:25:38,795 --> 00:25:39,659
Pawan, you kids know how to get there
巴萬

309
00:25:39,762 --> 00:25:41,957
你們幾個孩子知道路

310
00:25:42,065 --> 00:25:44,533
Take the Boarung women and children along
with those of us that are ready
帶外面那些波阿崙的女人孩子

311
00:25:44,634 --> 00:25:48,297
和這邊已經整理好的人先過去…

312
00:25:48,504 --> 00:25:50,597
Baso, I'm no longer a child
巴索，我已經不是孩子了！

313
00:25:52,609 --> 00:25:55,601
Don't let the dogs follow us
We don't have enough food
別讓狗跟著，我們食物不夠…

314
00:26:02,151 --> 00:26:03,175
Mahung, are you ready? Is it heavy?
馬紅…

315
00:26:03,286 --> 00:26:05,914
該帶的都帶了吧？很重嗎？

316
00:26:09,425 --> 00:26:10,187
Mahung, you go ahead with Pawan and others
馬紅

317
00:26:10,293 --> 00:26:12,955
你先和巴萬他們一起過去吧！

318
00:26:13,062 --> 00:26:14,996
I'll wait for Sapu
我等薩布…

319
00:26:15,098 --> 00:26:16,998
Why is everyone in here?
幹嘛都擠在這裡呢？

320
00:26:19,002 --> 00:26:20,867
Mother, don't touch that!
母親，那個不要動…

321
00:26:27,343 --> 00:26:31,109
You're out of your minds!
The men in this house have all gone mad
瘋了！我們家的男人全瘋了…

322
00:26:36,452 --> 00:26:37,612
Go ahead to Paran Clan, Obing
歐嬪…你跟他們去巴蘭社吧！

323
00:26:37,720 --> 00:26:39,244
No!
不要！不要！

324
00:26:39,355 --> 00:26:41,585
Jiro, let me stay with you
二郎…讓我留下來…

325
00:26:41,691 --> 00:26:43,921
Jiro!
二郎…二郎…

326
00:26:44,027 --> 00:26:46,587
Let go of me!
-All pregnant women go to Paran Clan
-不要拉我…
-有身孕的都去巴蘭社吧！

327
00:26:46,696 --> 00:26:49,722
Auntie, I'm the wife of a policeman
姑媽…我是警察的妻子…

328
00:26:49,832 --> 00:26:52,926
but I'm the daughter of the Gungu Chief as well
可是我也是荷戈社頭目的女兒呀…

329
00:26:53,036 --> 00:26:54,503
Auntie, let go of me!
姑媽…

330
00:26:54,604 --> 00:26:56,037
不要拉我…

331
00:26:56,139 --> 00:26:57,003
Give birth to your child in Paran Clan
-不要拉…
-去巴蘭社把孩子生下來…

332
00:26:57,106 --> 00:27:00,337
Jiro! I want to stay with you!
二郎…我要留下來…

333
00:27:00,443 --> 00:27:03,378
I don't want to go there, Auntie!
我不要走…姑媽…

334
00:27:03,479 --> 00:27:06,971
Give birth to your child in Paran Clan
我不要走…我要留下來…

335
00:27:09,719 --> 00:27:12,449
They're all pregnant
她們有身孕

336
00:27:12,555 --> 00:27:14,921
The Japanese won't harm them
日本人不會對她們怎樣的…

337
00:28:48,184 --> 00:28:49,173
Pawan!
巴萬…

338
00:28:50,586 --> 00:28:52,053
Pawan!
巴萬！

339
00:28:54,390 --> 00:28:55,482
What is it?
怎麼啦？

340
00:28:57,560 --> 00:28:59,619
The cavern is right up ahead
You can carry these over by yourselves
岩窟就在前面了

341
00:28:59,729 --> 00:29:02,789
這些東西你們可以搬得過去的…

342
00:29:03,966 --> 00:29:06,400
We have to go now
我們要先走了！

343
00:29:08,271 --> 00:29:09,863
But where to?
…走去哪裡啊？

344
00:29:15,511 --> 00:29:20,813
No, Mother! -Grandmother!
-不要啊…母親…
-祖母…

345
00:29:20,917 --> 00:29:24,648
Mother! -Grandmother!
-母親…
-祖母…

346
00:29:24,754 --> 00:29:26,984
No, Mother! -Grandmother!
-不要啊…母親…
-祖母…

347
00:29:27,089 --> 00:29:29,649
What are you doing?
你在幹什麼？你們在幹什麼啦…

348
00:29:29,759 --> 00:29:31,124
Mother, don't!
母親…不要…

349
00:29:31,227 --> 00:29:33,957
Grandmother! -What are you doing?
-祖母…祖母！
-你們幹什麼啦…

350
00:29:34,063 --> 00:29:37,464
Chief Mouna and others will be here soon
莫那頭目他們等一下就來了…

351
00:29:37,567 --> 00:29:41,970
Grandmother! -Mother!
-祖母…
-母親…

352
00:29:42,071 --> 00:29:46,633
You'll have to fight the Japanese for a long time
你們得跟日本人長期戰鬥…

353
00:29:46,742 --> 00:29:49,677
There's not enough food for all of us
這些存糧不夠那麼多人吃的！

354
00:29:49,779 --> 00:29:51,007
What are you talking about?
你亂講…

355
00:29:51,113 --> 00:29:54,014
Chief Mouna told us we're going to
fight our decisive battle soon
莫那頭目說很快就會決戰的…

356
00:29:54,116 --> 00:29:56,607
Grandmother!
祖母…

357
00:29:56,719 --> 00:29:57,879
Pawan!
巴萬…

358
00:29:59,222 --> 00:30:04,455
I'm so glad that you're a warrior now
guarding our hunting grounds
母親很高興你已是守護獵場的戰士

359
00:30:04,560 --> 00:30:07,529
We'll be waiting for you
at the other end of the rainbow bridge
我們先去彩虹的另一端等著你們！

360
00:30:07,630 --> 00:30:11,430
You'll be meeting us
after you finish your glorious battles
等著你們決戰之後，風光的回家…

361
00:30:11,534 --> 00:30:13,229
Stop following us!
不要跟來…

362
00:30:13,336 --> 00:30:15,861
Fight for your hunting grounds -Mother!
-為你的獵場戰鬥…
-母親…

363
00:30:15,972 --> 00:30:17,132
Grandmother, don't you want me anymore?
祖母…

364
00:30:17,240 --> 00:30:20,801
你怎麼不要我了…

365
00:30:20,910 --> 00:30:23,845
Mother!
母親…

366
00:30:23,946 --> 00:30:25,971
Mother!
母親…母親…

367
00:30:26,082 --> 00:30:28,812
Pawan, please tell my husband Watan
巴萬，請告訴我的丈夫瓦旦

368
00:30:28,918 --> 00:30:32,547
that I'll have the wine ready for him
at the other end of the rainbow bridge
我在彩虹那端把酒釀好等他過來…

369
00:30:32,655 --> 00:30:34,885
Watan is building up huts in the cavern
You can go tell him yourself
瓦旦就在岩窟搭草寮

370
00:30:34,991 --> 00:30:37,152
你自己去跟他講…

371
00:30:38,160 --> 00:30:40,219
Lubi! Lubi!
露比…露比…

372
00:30:40,329 --> 00:30:42,559
Stop following us! -Mother!
-不要跟來…
-母親…

373
00:30:42,665 --> 00:30:45,031
Don't follow us! -Mother, don't!
-不要跟來…
-母親不要…

374
00:30:45,134 --> 00:30:48,069
Please... -Mother!
-媽媽求你了…
-母親…

375
00:30:48,170 --> 00:30:50,502
Don't cry -Grandmother!
-不要哭…不要哭…
-祖母…

376
00:30:50,606 --> 00:30:52,699
Listen to me..
聽我說…

377
00:30:52,808 --> 00:30:55,333
you're a grownup man now
你現在已經是男人了…

378
00:30:55,444 --> 00:30:56,274
Go on!
去吧…

379
00:30:56,379 --> 00:30:58,677
Grandmother! -To the battlefield!
-祖母…
-去戰鬥吧！

380
00:30:58,781 --> 00:31:01,113
Fight for your hunting grounds!
-Grandmother!
-為你的獵場…用力戰鬥！
-祖母…

381
00:31:01,217 --> 00:31:02,514
To the battlefield!
去戰鬥…

382
00:31:05,354 --> 00:31:08,812
Grandmother!
祖母…

383
00:31:08,925 --> 00:31:10,984
Mother! -Grandmother!
-母親…
-祖母…

384
00:31:12,828 --> 00:31:14,887
Mother!
母親…

385
00:31:14,997 --> 00:31:16,828
Mother!
母親…

386
00:31:16,933 --> 00:31:22,371
Don't go, Mother! -Grandmother!
-不要走呀…母親…
-祖母…

387
00:31:25,608 --> 00:31:27,371
Mother..
母親…

388
00:31:29,845 --> 00:31:38,719
With tears in my eyes
我眼中含淚

389
00:31:38,821 --> 00:31:47,160
l'm walking along a wide road
沿著寬廣的路前進

390
00:31:47,263 --> 00:31:56,137
l beseech you
我懇求你們

391
00:31:56,238 --> 00:32:05,169
Tell me if your hearts are at peace
你們甘心嗎？

392
00:32:05,281 --> 00:32:14,246
Oh, poor innocent children
孩子們是多麼的可憐啊…

393
00:32:14,357 --> 00:32:23,231
What's the matter with you?
你們是怎麼了呢？

394
00:32:23,332 --> 00:32:31,865
We're really exhausted
我們真的非常地疲累…

395
00:33:35,371 --> 00:33:36,633
Hanako?
花子…

396
00:33:41,143 --> 00:33:46,740
You look just as pretty
as you were on our wedding day
你還是跟我們結婚時一樣漂亮…

397
00:34:16,011 --> 00:34:24,146
Good boy! Close your eyes!
乖…眼睛閉起來…

398
00:34:58,454 --> 00:35:03,391
My child, let's go together
孩子…我們一起走吧…

399
00:36:11,293 --> 00:36:12,453
Jiro?
二郎…

400
00:36:13,963 --> 00:36:16,932
Are we the subjects of Japan's Mikado?
我們到底該是日本天皇的子民？

401
00:36:18,534 --> 00:36:20,968
Or the descendants of the Seediq ancestors?
還是賽德克祖靈的子孫？

402
00:36:24,840 --> 00:36:27,070
Do it
…切開吧！

403
00:36:27,176 --> 00:36:30,077
Cut it up and end your conflicts
right here and now
一刀切開你矛盾的肝腸吧…

404
00:36:30,179 --> 00:36:32,943
We don't have to go anywhere once we're dead
哪兒也別去了…

405
00:36:33,048 --> 00:36:35,448
Let's both be free wandering spirits
當個自在的遊魂吧！

406
00:36:50,866 --> 00:36:52,458
Thank you
謝謝…

407
00:38:01,937 --> 00:38:04,064
This way please, General
司令，這邊請…

408
00:38:15,050 --> 00:38:17,518
This is Officer Kabasoa, sir
司令，這位是樺澤警部

409
00:38:17,619 --> 00:38:19,314
He's a local policeman
and he knows the Wushe savages very well
是此地的警察

410
00:38:19,421 --> 00:38:21,252
對霧社地區的蕃情相當熟悉…

411
00:38:21,357 --> 00:38:23,757
Then why are you still alive?
那你為什麼還活著？

412
00:38:26,161 --> 00:38:30,063
He was not there when the incident happened
…他當時不在公學校

413
00:38:40,576 --> 00:38:41,474
General, according to our investigation
司令

414
00:38:41,577 --> 00:38:42,737
根據我們的察訪

415
00:38:42,845 --> 00:38:44,540
there are six clans involved in the revolt
over 300 warriors in all
參與反抗的部落有六個

416
00:38:44,646 --> 00:38:46,443
共有三百多名戰士…

417
00:38:47,616 --> 00:38:48,548
Warriors?
戰士？

418
00:38:50,619 --> 00:38:52,746
You call them 'warriors'
你稱他們為戰士…

419
00:38:54,289 --> 00:38:57,816
Each of these clans took actions separately
他們在凌晨時，各部落單獨行動

420
00:38:57,926 --> 00:38:59,450
at dawn and annihilated
the local police stations
殲滅當地駐在所之後

421
00:38:59,561 --> 00:39:02,291
Then they got together to besiege Wushe
再一起集合圍攻霧社

422
00:39:02,398 --> 00:39:05,492
That's why we don't think it incidental
所以我們判斷這絕不是突發事件

423
00:39:05,601 --> 00:39:08,866
They had been planning it carefully
from the beginning
而是一開始就經過詳細的計劃！

424
00:39:10,773 --> 00:39:14,072
Planning it carefully?
詳細計劃？

425
00:39:14,176 --> 00:39:16,303
Mr. Kabasoa?
樺澤先生…

426
00:39:16,412 --> 00:39:19,404
Don't you think
you're overestimating these savages?
你會不會太高估了這些野蠻人？

427
00:39:19,515 --> 00:39:23,884
General, all our reinforcements
were under fatal attacks yesterday
司令…昨天我們各個支援的部隊

428
00:39:23,986 --> 00:39:26,284
都遭到了嚴重的突擊…

429
00:39:27,156 --> 00:39:28,953
...including here
包括這裡…

430
00:39:38,901 --> 00:39:43,065
This is nothing but animal-like savagery
這只是動物性的野蠻行為…

431
00:39:45,974 --> 00:39:49,910
Once the rain stops,
we'll besiege them immediately
等雨一停，立刻圍攻部落！

432
00:39:50,012 --> 00:39:50,706
Yes, sir!
是！

433
00:39:53,716 --> 00:39:59,716
(Headquarters of Kamada Detachment)

434
00:40:48,103 --> 00:40:49,331
Chief,
頭目…

435
00:40:49,438 --> 00:40:52,430
are we going for the decisive battle tomorrow?
明天要決戰了嗎？

436
00:41:10,425 --> 00:41:11,790
Ah, it hurts!
啊…痛啊…

437
00:41:11,894 --> 00:41:15,830
Chief, the wounds are still fresh
頭目…傷口還沒好哪…

438
00:41:24,406 --> 00:41:25,270
Pawan, you're not a child anymore
巴萬

439
00:41:26,275 --> 00:41:28,140
你已經不是個孩子了！

440
00:41:33,148 --> 00:41:34,240
Chief, can we fight the decisive battle now?
…頭目

441
00:41:35,551 --> 00:41:38,543
我們快點決戰好不好？

442
00:42:07,783 --> 00:42:08,511
What's happening?
發生什麼事…

443
00:42:09,785 --> 00:42:10,774
Give me the gun!
槍給我…

444
00:42:11,954 --> 00:42:13,444
Hurry up!
快…快點…

445
00:42:19,828 --> 00:42:21,853
Let's go!
走！

446
00:42:33,041 --> 00:42:34,133
Hurry up!
快點！

447
00:42:35,410 --> 00:42:36,308
Be careful!
小心！

448
00:42:37,613 --> 00:42:38,875
Go over there! Be careful!
你們過去那邊！

449
00:42:38,981 --> 00:42:40,608
小心一點！

450
00:42:50,826 --> 00:42:51,793
Stop! The savages!
停下來！

451
00:42:51,893 --> 00:42:53,622
有兇蕃！

452
00:43:00,202 --> 00:43:01,499
Stop running!
不要跑！

453
00:43:09,845 --> 00:43:11,005
Over there!
在那邊…

454
00:43:17,052 --> 00:43:18,451
What the hell?
在搞什麼東西啊？

455
00:43:23,759 --> 00:43:24,726
Fire!
開槍！

456
00:43:29,698 --> 00:43:30,858
Retreat! All retreat!
撤退…

457
00:43:30,966 --> 00:43:34,959
全部撤退…

458
00:43:39,241 --> 00:43:40,708
Hurry up and run!
快點…大家快跑…

459
00:43:59,995 --> 00:44:03,226
Seek covers! -Down there!
往下面去…找掩護…

460
00:44:05,000 --> 00:44:06,490
Signalman, call for reinforcements
通訊兵，快通報支援…

461
00:44:07,803 --> 00:44:09,031
Retreat downhill! Hide!
往下撤退…

462
00:44:09,137 --> 00:44:10,570
躲起來…

463
00:44:11,239 --> 00:44:13,002
Out of the way!
讓開！讓開！

464
00:44:43,271 --> 00:44:44,738
Watch out!
後面小心…

465
00:44:45,507 --> 00:44:47,600
Quite slippery here
這邊很滑…

466
00:44:52,414 --> 00:44:53,745
Are you alright?
還好嗎？

467
00:44:53,849 --> 00:44:56,784
Halt, everyone!
前面隊伍停下來…

468
00:45:09,364 --> 00:45:11,628
Jump!
跳下去！

469
00:45:47,569 --> 00:45:48,900
Machine gun!
機關槍…機關槍…

470
00:45:49,004 --> 00:45:49,902
Step back! -Take aim!
-向後退！
-打那邊一點…

471
00:45:50,005 --> 00:45:51,199
You're aiming too high! Hold on to your guns!
你打太高了！槍拿穩…

472
00:45:52,240 --> 00:45:54,470
Come on, fire it,
Sapu! What are you waiting for?
快打呀薩布！等什麼？

473
00:45:54,576 --> 00:45:56,407
I can't fire it
打不出去呀…

474
00:46:00,115 --> 00:46:01,241
Move over! I'll do it!
讓開我來！

475
00:46:03,018 --> 00:46:05,009
Come on! Hurry up!
快跑…快一點…

476
00:46:05,754 --> 00:46:07,745
What the hell? Fell asleep or something?
搞什麼？睡著了啊？

477
00:46:09,057 --> 00:46:10,285
Over there! Come on!
那邊…快點…

478
00:46:10,392 --> 00:46:11,620
He's gone!
跑掉了…

479
00:46:12,394 --> 00:46:15,022
If I aim at the rock deliberately
如果我故意打在石頭上

480
00:46:15,130 --> 00:46:17,860
will the bullet bounce off
and hit the officer over there?
子彈會反彈到後面那個軍官嗎？

481
00:46:18,767 --> 00:46:19,927
Why don't you give it a try?
你試試看…

482
00:46:24,005 --> 00:46:26,633
No, it won't
不行啦…沒有用…

483
00:46:26,741 --> 00:46:29,972
Have you two got too many bullets?
你們兩個子彈太多是不是？

484
00:46:30,078 --> 00:46:31,010
No, but that is a military officer
with a katana sword
不是呀…

485
00:46:31,112 --> 00:46:33,876
那是個軍官哪…帶刀的！

486
00:46:43,024 --> 00:46:43,854
Chief, Tado robbed a couple of machineguns
頭目…

487
00:46:43,959 --> 00:46:46,621
達多搶到了兩挺機槍

488
00:46:46,728 --> 00:46:49,788
Chief Mouna asked us to bring you one and..
莫那頭目叫我們送一挺來給你們…

489
00:46:49,898 --> 00:46:51,331
還有…

490
00:46:51,433 --> 00:46:53,924
here's the ammunition and..
這是彈藥…還有…

491
00:46:54,035 --> 00:46:55,900
and this bag of sweet potatoes
還有這些地瓜…

492
00:46:57,539 --> 00:47:00,372
Kids nowadays are so weak
現在的孩子怎麼這麼沒用啊？

493
00:47:00,475 --> 00:47:03,672
Look how they pant with so little running
才跑沒多遠就喘成這樣！

494
00:47:05,347 --> 00:47:07,247
Do you know how to use it?
這東西你會弄嗎？

495
00:47:09,251 --> 00:47:12,618
I don't think this machinegun works
這機槍好像打不出去…

496
00:47:15,957 --> 00:47:18,619
Why did you give me one that doesn't work?
拿個打不出去的機槍給我幹嘛？

497
00:47:22,797 --> 00:47:24,924
That damned Mouna!
莫那這傢伙…

498
00:47:28,136 --> 00:47:29,296
Chief Dahdo..
塔道頭目

499
00:47:30,605 --> 00:47:32,971
My Paran relatives told me..
我聽到我巴蘭社的親戚說…

500
00:47:35,377 --> 00:47:38,835
that your entire family committed suicide
…你整個頭目家族全都自盡了…

501
00:47:46,621 --> 00:47:47,485
Chief Dahdo, a bigger and more powerful army
is coming our way
塔道頭目…

502
00:47:47,589 --> 00:47:50,922
更大更多的軍隊往這裡圍過來了…

503
00:47:51,026 --> 00:47:52,960
They have lots of cannons
還有好多的大砲！

504
00:48:06,741 --> 00:48:07,605
Pawan, when I was young
巴萬…

505
00:48:08,677 --> 00:48:10,076
我年輕時的威風…

506
00:48:10,178 --> 00:48:13,306
I was no less strong or brave
than your Mehebu Chief Mouna Rudo
可不輸給你們馬赫坡的莫那魯道

507
00:48:13,415 --> 00:48:14,746
you understand?
你懂嗎？

508
00:48:18,620 --> 00:48:19,552
Awi, lead the group and retreat to Rkudaya
阿威…

509
00:48:20,755 --> 00:48:23,553
等一下帶大家退到魯庫達亞…

510
00:48:28,563 --> 00:48:29,427
Chief!
頭目…

511
00:48:29,531 --> 00:48:31,522
Chief!
頭目…

512
00:48:38,039 --> 00:48:39,768
Chief! Chief!
頭目…頭目…

513
00:48:42,711 --> 00:48:44,770
Retreat! To Rkudaya!
退！退到魯庫達亞…

514
00:48:44,879 --> 00:48:46,107
Give it to me! Let's go!
拿過來…快走…

515
00:48:46,214 --> 00:48:48,580
Retreat to Rkudaya! Our chief's dead!
快退到魯庫達亞…頭目死了…

516
00:48:48,683 --> 00:48:51,277
Come on!
…快點！

517
00:48:53,655 --> 00:48:55,680
Pihu, come on!
比荷…快點！

518
00:49:04,933 --> 00:49:06,992
Retreat to Rkudaya!
退到魯庫達亞…

519
00:49:07,102 --> 00:49:09,366
Come on! To Rkudaya!
快點！往魯庫達亞！

520
00:49:09,471 --> 00:49:11,666
Come on! Let's go!
快點！快點！

521
00:49:12,607 --> 00:49:13,801
Fire!
發射！

522
00:49:18,046 --> 00:49:19,741
Chase them!
追擊！

523
00:49:21,916 --> 00:49:22,746
Come on!
快！

524
00:49:23,885 --> 00:49:24,874
Come on!
快一點！

525
00:50:11,633 --> 00:50:14,329
Run in separate ways!
Let's meet up in Rkudaya!
分開跑…往魯庫達亞集合…

526
00:50:15,437 --> 00:50:17,962
Hurry up! Come on!
快點…快點…

527
00:50:35,790 --> 00:50:37,018
Awi, come on!
阿威，快！

528
00:50:37,125 --> 00:50:38,183
Here comes the airplane again!
飛機又來了…

529
00:50:46,835 --> 00:50:48,166
Why is Pihu still there?
比荷怎麼還在那邊？

530
00:50:50,772 --> 00:50:51,534
Come on!
快過去…

531
00:51:01,783 --> 00:51:03,546
Hurry up, Pihu!
比荷，快點！

532
00:51:03,651 --> 00:51:05,585
The bridge is collapsing!
橋要斷了…

533
00:51:13,495 --> 00:51:15,360
Come on, the bridge is collapsing!
快一點…橋要倒下來了…

534
00:51:27,008 --> 00:51:28,942
Medic! Medic!
衛生兵！衛生兵！

535
00:51:29,043 --> 00:51:31,136
Hurry up!
走快一點…

536
00:51:38,953 --> 00:51:40,420
Hurry up!
走快一點…

537
00:51:42,223 --> 00:51:46,091
No matter which route we took
we were ambushed by them
不管哪個路線都會掉進他們的埋伏

538
00:51:46,194 --> 00:51:49,493
好像他們早就猜到我們的行動一樣

539
00:51:49,597 --> 00:51:51,724
These savages are too good at this
這些兇蕃太厲害了

540
00:51:51,833 --> 00:51:53,994
We should ask for more reinforcements,
otherwise..
我們應該再增兵支援

541
00:51:54,102 --> 00:51:54,830
否則…

542
00:51:57,205 --> 00:52:00,697
With thousands of soldiers
and all kinds of powerful weapons
幾千名火力強大的武裝部隊

543
00:52:01,743 --> 00:52:06,544
and you ended up being toyed with
by 300 savages?
竟被三百個生蕃給耍得團團轉？

544
00:52:07,749 --> 00:52:12,812
Our airplanes have been patrolling
and bombing all this time
我們飛機在天空飛半天、轟半天…

545
00:52:12,921 --> 00:52:15,651
without killing any savage
為何就是打不到人…

546
00:52:16,758 --> 00:52:20,956
And you call yourselves military officers?
你們這些軍官到底是幹什麼吃的？

547
00:52:33,141 --> 00:52:37,202
Those savages played hit and run
這些兇蕃打了就跑…

548
00:52:37,312 --> 00:52:39,906
They're like ghosts
像鬼一樣…

549
00:52:40,648 --> 00:52:42,639
They ran easily
over the ragged mountain paths
在連站都站不穩的山路上…

550
00:52:42,750 --> 00:52:44,479
that we barely walked properly on
跑起來像飛的一樣

551
00:52:44,586 --> 00:52:47,646
We never knew where they came from
or where they disappeared to
不知道從哪裡來也不知道往哪裡去

552
00:52:47,755 --> 00:52:50,019
They were so unpredictable
完全無法預料呀…

553
00:52:51,426 --> 00:52:53,394
For example, a kid named Pawan Nawi..
像一個叫巴萬那威的孩子

554
00:52:54,462 --> 00:52:57,022
We saw him here the day before yesterday
but we found him here yesterday
前天在這個地方看到

555
00:52:57,131 --> 00:52:59,292
昨天又在這裡被發現

556
00:52:59,400 --> 00:53:02,096
Then he was here today
今天又變到這個地方來了

557
00:53:03,338 --> 00:53:06,432
These are three different places
far away from one another
這些地方距離都那麼遠

558
00:53:06,541 --> 00:53:08,941
No one knows how he managed to do so
這孩子是怎麼跑到的？

559
00:53:10,278 --> 00:53:12,007
…真的搞不懂！

560
00:53:21,155 --> 00:53:22,986
Pawan, have you fought any battle?
巴萬，你們打仗了嗎？

561
00:53:23,958 --> 00:53:25,186
Pawan! -Chief Mouna!
-巴萬…
-莫那頭目…

562
00:53:29,697 --> 00:53:34,464
Chief Dahdo Nokan from Gungu Clan
was killed in a battle
荷戈社的塔道諾幹頭目…

563
00:53:35,570 --> 00:53:37,697
戰死了！

564
00:53:51,586 --> 00:53:53,850
Has anyone seen Mouna Rudo yet?
莫那魯道出現了嗎？

565
00:53:59,460 --> 00:54:00,484
Answer me! -No, sir
回答！

566
00:54:00,595 --> 00:54:01,459
沒有…

567
00:54:02,730 --> 00:54:05,221
That old bastard!
這死老烏龜…

568
00:54:05,767 --> 00:54:07,894
He had the guts to revolt
but he dares not confront me personally
有種造反…

569
00:54:08,002 --> 00:54:11,665
卻沒種出來和我決一死戰

570
00:54:11,773 --> 00:54:14,606
What kind of warrior is he?
What kind of chief is he?
算什麼戰士！算什麼頭目！

571
00:54:17,345 --> 00:54:18,710
Be quiet!
安靜！

572
00:54:30,992 --> 00:54:33,290
They've got lines and lines of defense
and endless reinforcement
一道又一道的防線

573
00:54:33,394 --> 00:54:37,990
怎麼切都切不斷的支援線路…

574
00:54:39,701 --> 00:54:42,135
I can't believe those savages
would have battle plans so well-knit
這樣粗魯的野蠻人

575
00:54:43,104 --> 00:54:47,131
竟然有如此綿密的作戰計畫…

576
00:54:56,451 --> 00:54:59,511
Ask the high command to provide us
with gas bombs
向軍司令部申請糜爛性砲彈！

577
00:54:59,620 --> 00:55:02,418
Gas bombs?
糜爛性砲彈？

578
00:55:06,361 --> 00:55:09,626
I wanted you to be civilized
叫你們文明…

579
00:55:09,731 --> 00:55:12,757
but you forced me to be savage
你們卻逼我野蠻！

580
00:55:19,240 --> 00:55:22,073
You're Mouna Rudo
你是莫那魯道…

581
00:55:25,079 --> 00:55:27,479
but I'm Kamada Yahiko
我可是鎌田彌彥！

582
00:55:28,850 --> 00:55:31,819
From now on..
從現在開始

583
00:55:31,919 --> 00:55:40,554
you're part of the Japanese
military and police forces
你們就屬於大日本帝國軍警隊的一員

584
00:55:40,661 --> 00:55:44,563
You'll have to follow our wartime decrees
今後對軍警的戰地勒令要絕對服從

585
00:55:44,665 --> 00:55:47,156
Those of you who fight bravely
will be rewarded accordingly
對於勇武善戰者…

586
00:55:47,268 --> 00:55:49,429
我們會給予獎賞

587
00:55:50,304 --> 00:55:52,204
But those of you
但是…

588
00:55:52,306 --> 00:55:58,836
who fail to take orders from
the Japanese police or run away
如果不遵從日本警察的命令…

589
00:55:58,946 --> 00:56:03,144
will be punished harshly by law
臨陣脫逃者，絕對依法嚴辦！

590
00:56:03,985 --> 00:56:05,350
Do you understand?
明白了沒？

591
00:56:07,121 --> 00:56:11,080
Now I'm announcing
the bounties of head-hunting
我現在宣布獵首獎金…

592
00:56:15,797 --> 00:56:18,732
We'll give every one of you a gun
我們會發給每個人一把槍！

593
00:56:24,605 --> 00:56:28,701
Come and sign for it after this
等一下每個人都過來登記！

594
00:56:36,484 --> 00:56:37,610
A chief.. 150 to 200 dollars
頭目…

595
00:56:38,619 --> 00:56:43,181
一百五十元到兩百元不等…

596
00:56:43,324 --> 00:56:46,691
An able-bodied man, 100
壯丁…一百元！

597
00:56:49,163 --> 00:56:52,792
A woman, 30
婦女…三十元！

598
00:56:52,900 --> 00:56:55,835
A child, 20
小孩…二十元！

599
00:56:57,572 --> 00:56:59,267
And a special bounty for the head of..
…特別獎

600
00:57:09,217 --> 00:57:10,650
...Mouna Rudo!
莫那魯道

601
00:57:27,368 --> 00:57:28,562
Gas bombs?
糜爛性砲彈？

602
00:57:34,909 --> 00:57:36,399
But sir,
報告…

603
00:57:37,411 --> 00:57:40,676
Gas bombs are still being experimented on
這種炸彈還在實驗階段…

604
00:57:40,781 --> 00:57:42,749
We don't know the effects yet
效果如何也還不知道…

605
00:57:43,417 --> 00:57:44,509
Yes, sir
是…

606
00:57:45,720 --> 00:57:47,244
Yes, sir
是…

607
00:57:47,788 --> 00:57:50,621
But currently it's not ready for use
…可是目前真的不適合…

608
00:57:50,725 --> 00:57:52,659
Yes, sir
是…

609
00:57:52,760 --> 00:57:53,419
Yes, sir
是…

610
00:58:52,653 --> 00:58:54,280
Come on!
快一點…

611
00:58:56,490 --> 00:58:57,889
Watan, you go that way!
瓦旦，你們往那邊…

612
00:59:11,205 --> 00:59:11,967
Sapu!
薩布！

613
00:59:13,374 --> 00:59:15,274
I'm alright. They hit my sweet potatoes
我沒事！地瓜擋著哪…

614
00:59:24,919 --> 00:59:26,978
Don't stop! Run!
不要停下來，快跑…

615
00:59:31,492 --> 00:59:33,756
Shoot! Shoot him!
快開槍…射他！

616
00:59:33,861 --> 00:59:35,192
Come on!
快！

617
00:59:42,837 --> 00:59:44,202
Out of the way!
不要擋路！

618
01:00:15,236 --> 01:00:16,669
Over there!
那邊！在那邊！

619
01:00:39,393 --> 01:00:41,122
A Seediq from Tgdaya! -Where?
-德克達亞人！
-在哪裡？

620
01:00:41,228 --> 01:00:42,286
He's over there!
跑到那邊了…

621
01:00:42,930 --> 01:00:43,919
Kill him!
殺了他！

622
01:01:47,161 --> 01:01:48,856
Burn it down!
燒掉…

623
01:02:43,818 --> 01:02:44,842
Temu!
泰目…

624
01:03:15,082 --> 01:03:16,640
Come on! Run!
快跑…快跑…

625
01:05:53,874 --> 01:05:55,102
Chief Mouna! It's me, Pawan
莫那頭目

626
01:05:55,209 --> 01:05:56,437
我是巴萬啊…

627
01:05:59,546 --> 01:06:00,911
Chief Mouna! It's me, Pawan Nawi
莫那頭目…

628
01:06:01,015 --> 01:06:02,812
是我，巴萬那威啊…

629
01:06:21,735 --> 01:06:23,066
Chief Mouna, we heard what Baso told you
莫那頭目…

630
01:06:23,137 --> 01:06:25,799
我們有聽到巴索和你說的話…

631
01:06:25,906 --> 01:06:30,138
We know that a large number of
Japanese soldiers have gathered in Suku Clan
大批日軍已經由斯庫社集結…

632
01:06:30,244 --> 01:06:32,940
Time for the decisive battle, isn't it?
是決戰的時侯了吧！

633
01:06:39,753 --> 01:06:40,981
Chief Mouna, we have no family now
Why don't you let us fight?
莫那頭目

634
01:06:41,088 --> 01:06:42,817
我們都已經沒有家人了

635
01:06:42,923 --> 01:06:45,050
為什麼你就不讓我們去打仗呢？

636
01:06:45,159 --> 01:06:46,751
Like everyone else, none of us can sleep or eat
我們和大家一樣…

637
01:06:46,860 --> 01:06:50,318
每天吃不飽、睡不飽

638
01:06:50,431 --> 01:06:54,424
and we don't want to be killed by gas bombs
可是我們真的不想被毒炸彈炸死…

639
01:07:00,774 --> 01:07:02,139
Chief Mouna, look at the tattoos on our faces
We're not children anymore
莫那頭目

640
01:07:02,242 --> 01:07:03,709
你看我們臉上的圖騰

641
01:07:03,811 --> 01:07:05,745
我們已經不是孩子了…

642
01:07:05,846 --> 01:07:07,507
Please let us fight the Japanese
like everybody else
你就讓我們和大家一樣

643
01:07:07,614 --> 01:07:09,775
用力和日本人打一仗吧！

644
01:07:13,153 --> 01:07:15,519
Then I can have a good, long rest
我想好好睡個覺…

645
01:07:16,690 --> 01:07:20,148
We're so tired
我們好累…

646
01:07:20,260 --> 01:07:23,195
We're really exhausted
我們真的好累…

647
01:07:44,351 --> 01:07:45,340
My children, do you remember
where our ancestors came from?
孩子們…

648
01:07:46,220 --> 01:07:48,245
還記得我們的祖先從哪來的嗎？

649
01:07:48,355 --> 01:07:49,185
Mt. White Stone.. -I know. Once upon a time...
-Let me tell the story!
白石山…

650
01:07:49,289 --> 01:07:50,017
-我知道…從前…
-我來講…

651
01:07:50,124 --> 01:07:51,352
Quiet!
安靜！

652
01:07:53,026 --> 01:07:54,391
Can't you wait?
急什麼？

653
01:07:56,363 --> 01:08:00,163
A good hunter should learn how to lie in wait!
好獵人要學會安靜等待！

654
01:08:02,302 --> 01:08:03,826
Pawan, you tell the story
巴萬你講…

655
01:08:12,246 --> 01:08:14,271
Once upon a time on Mt. White Stone
there was a big tree called Pusu Qhuni
從前從前在白石山上…

656
01:08:14,381 --> 01:08:19,512
有一棵大樹，名叫波索康夫尼…

657
01:08:19,620 --> 01:08:21,281
The tree trunk was half wood, half stone
他的樹身…

658
01:08:21,388 --> 01:08:25,324
一半是木頭，另一半是岩石…

659
01:08:25,425 --> 01:08:32,627
One day, a boy and a girl were born
from the tree trunk
有一天，他的樹身生下了一男一女

660
01:08:32,733 --> 01:08:35,634
Then the couple gave birth to lots of children
後來這男女又生下了許多的孩子…

661
01:08:35,736 --> 01:08:39,729
and here we are, the Seediq Bale
就是我們…真正的賽德克人…

662
01:09:07,634 --> 01:09:10,102
Let me help you, Awi
阿威，我幫你吧！

663
01:09:13,640 --> 01:09:15,904
It's ready, my brother
兄弟，準備好了…

664
01:09:40,400 --> 01:09:41,458
I'm ready
可以了…

665
01:09:47,241 --> 01:09:50,176
Let go, my brother
放手吧！兄弟…

666
01:09:50,277 --> 01:09:51,972
Pihu Walis..
比荷瓦力斯…

667
01:09:52,913 --> 01:09:54,244
Don't go! -Let go!
-你不要走…
-放手吧！

668
01:09:54,915 --> 01:09:56,849
I'm in great pain
我真的好痛苦…

669
01:09:56,950 --> 01:09:58,611
Don't go
不要走…

670
01:10:27,547 --> 01:10:29,071
I'm not fighting anymore! No more!
我不要打了…

671
01:10:29,182 --> 01:10:30,706
不打了！

672
01:10:30,817 --> 01:10:32,250
No more!
不打了…

673
01:10:32,352 --> 01:10:33,341
You son of a bitch!
混蛋！

674
01:10:34,688 --> 01:10:36,622
What do you mean by not fighting?
-Kojima!
你說不打了是什麼意思？

675
01:10:36,723 --> 01:10:37,382
小島…

676
01:10:37,491 --> 01:10:39,652
What do you mean by that? -Kojima!
-不打了是什麼意思？
-小島…

677
01:10:39,760 --> 01:10:40,727
Pick it up! Pick up your gun!
撿起來…

678
01:10:40,827 --> 01:10:41,885
把槍給我撿起來！

679
01:10:41,995 --> 01:10:43,519
Out of my way! -Temu!
-走開…
-鐵木…

680
01:10:44,064 --> 01:10:44,962
Temu!
鐵木…

681
01:10:48,869 --> 01:10:52,862
We fight to offer blood sacrifice to our ancestors
我們戰鬥…是為了血祭祖靈

682
01:10:53,607 --> 01:10:57,008
not to revenge the death of your family
不是替你死去的家人報復！

683
01:11:15,729 --> 01:11:17,253
Temu, I know what you saw
鐵木…

684
01:11:17,364 --> 01:11:20,162
我知道你看見了什麼…

685
01:11:20,267 --> 01:11:24,499
but Mouna Rudo has spread the word
asking for your head
但莫那魯道已經放話要拿你人頭了…

686
01:11:24,604 --> 01:11:27,630
This is not the time to make trouble
現在不是惹麻煩的時侯…

687
01:11:46,293 --> 01:11:47,954
Father, you told me only the bravest warriors
父親…

688
01:11:48,061 --> 01:11:51,497
你說過，最美麗的獵場…

689
01:11:51,598 --> 01:11:55,932
are qualified to guard
the most beautiful hunting ground
只有最勇敢的戰士才夠資格去守護

690
01:11:56,036 --> 01:11:57,936
So that's why Mouna Rudo's people and we
have to fight one another constantly
那我們和莫那魯道他們…

691
01:11:58,038 --> 01:12:00,700
是不是要不斷地互相戰鬥…

692
01:12:00,807 --> 01:12:06,439
to prove to our ancestors
that we're the bravest warriors?
才能向祖靈證明自己是最勇武的戰士？

693
01:12:12,452 --> 01:12:14,977
So in the eternal hunting ground
at the other end of the rainbow
那在彩虹頂端的美麗獵場裡…

694
01:12:15,088 --> 01:12:18,524
we'll become allies forever
and there would be no more hatred?
大家是不是就成為永遠的戰友…

695
01:12:18,625 --> 01:12:21,150
不會再有仇恨了？

696
01:12:23,463 --> 01:12:24,760
Yeah, I guess so
…應該是吧！

697
01:12:25,699 --> 01:12:28,896
I want to fight them if possible
to prove my bravery
如果可以的話我也想和他們打一仗

698
01:12:29,002 --> 01:12:31,562
來證明我的武勇…

699
01:12:33,573 --> 01:12:34,835
Sleep, my boy
快睡吧！

700
01:14:02,963 --> 01:14:04,726
Is that our man?
那是我們的人嗎？

701
01:14:08,301 --> 01:14:15,366
Get him! He's a savage! Come on!
快點攔下那個蕃人…快點…

702
01:14:16,309 --> 01:14:17,901
Stop!
不要跑！

703
01:14:19,379 --> 01:14:20,505
Stop!
不要跑！

704
01:14:21,114 --> 01:14:21,978
What's wrong?
怎麼了？

705
01:14:22,082 --> 01:14:24,448
A savage ran over the suspension bridge
into the woods
有個蕃人從吊橋跑進樹林裡了！

706
01:14:27,687 --> 01:14:29,382
From there? -Yes, from there
-從那邊嗎？
-對，那邊！

707
01:14:31,391 --> 01:14:32,449
Gather up!
集合！

708
01:14:32,559 --> 01:14:34,151
Gather up, First Team!
第一部隊集合…

709
01:14:34,261 --> 01:14:35,489
Gather up!
集合…

710
01:14:35,595 --> 01:14:36,926
First Team!
第一部隊！

711
01:14:41,801 --> 01:14:43,098
Stop!
不要跑！

712
01:14:50,577 --> 01:14:52,169
Good
很好…

713
01:14:52,279 --> 01:14:54,042
Come closer..
再過來…再過來一點…

714
01:14:54,147 --> 01:14:55,842
Good
很好…

715
01:14:55,949 --> 01:14:57,814
Stop, you little bastard
