莫那魯道…

49
00:08:04,925 --> 00:08:05,892
Stop running!
大家不要逃了！

50
00:08:07,428 --> 00:08:09,225
Kill until our blood runs out!
殺到血乾吧…

51
00:08:09,730 --> 00:08:12,096
Cut off their heads like true warriors!
像戰士一樣拿下人頭…

52
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:15,634
The heavenly home of our ancestors,
here we come!
回祖靈之家唷…

53
00:10:25,866 --> 00:10:27,857
